    <data name="AboutDescription" xml:space="preserve"><value>Database Starter is a portable desktop application for managing local database servers on Windows. It allows you to download, install, start, and stop MySQL, MariaDB, and PostgreSQL as portable instances — without administrator privileges and without Windows services.
All database files are stored in the local user directory and can be completely removed at any time. The configuration is automatically persisted in a JSON file.
The application is aimed at developers who need quick and easy local database instances for development and testing.
Built with WPF and .NET 10.0.</value></data>
